{"tid":1144211,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"最重要係人品 JYP放棄X101尹書彬","createTime":"2019-05-08T03:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T08:41:59.000Z","uid":74065,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"af7e25443df72cd96736351dfc42340288c691aa","tid":1144211,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:09:07.000Z","msg":"據悉早前捲入校園暴力等爭議的Mnet選秀節目《#ProduceX101#》練習生#尹書彬#與經紀公司JYP解除練習生合約，也將從101節目下車。JYP方面今日向媒體發佈通稿表示「根據JYP方面判斷，因不符合公司的方針，我司決定與目前正在出演Mnet《ProduceX101》的尹書彬解除練習生合同，因此他也將從節目中下車」。尹書彬早前曾在首播的節目中露面，但5日有網友在網絡論壇等地留言，曝光尹書彬的過往，公開其畢業照，並主張尹書彬學生時期就是當地混混，經常使用校園暴力，該網友還曬出了尹書彬身穿校服抽煙的照片等，帖子一出很快便引發了輿論正義。<br />\n屌你牙JYP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f663dc47d036d4d7a1d20f83359b19212e6985e","tid":1144211,"uid":74065,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tJp38Cr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtJp38Cr.jpg&h=c623b801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJYP定必改正佢既過錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047fa99065e3a190ee5ea4097c6f21ebd228285a","tid":1144211,"uid":223790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:12:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11c3284ef00c1dd3d827a39ac0667d3720381479","tid":1144211,"uid":223790,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:13:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c185f43f84a78ca63fc7bcb070f9ebf05bfd4965","tid":1144211,"uid":89931,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:16:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ho ball 垃圾就應該踢走佢"},{"pid":"e4d9de0c4d9ea6980335e27caff822738ab1b802","tid":1144211,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c185f43f84a78ca63fc7bcb070f9ebf05bfd4965","tid":1144211,"uid":89931,"like":3,"dislike"